    </h4>
    <ul class="govuk-list">
      <li>
        Week 2: using examples and non-examples
      </li>
      <li>
        Week 5: using questioning to extend and challenge pupils
      </li>
    </ul>
    <h4 class="govuk-heading-s govuk-!-margin-bottom-2">
      <%= govuk_link_to "Second half-term: : how can you use assessment and feedback to greatest effect? (PDF, 181 KB, 5 pages)",
                        "/cip-materials/teach-first-ECF-Module-4-ECT-training-basic-programme-session-plan.pdf" %>
    </h4>
    <ul class="govuk-list">
      <li>
        Week 2: structuring questioning to anticipate and identify misconceptions
      </li>
      <li>
        Week 5: peer and self assessment
      </li>
    </ul>

    <hr class="govuk-section-break govuk-section-break--l govuk-section-break--visible">

    <h3 class="govuk-heading-m govuk-!-margin-top-4">Summer term</h3>

    <h4 class="govuk-heading-s govuk-!-margin-bottom-2">
      <%= govuk_link_to "First half-term: how can you support all pupils to succeed? (PDF, 191 KB, 5 pages)",
